WEBVTT

00:00.830 --> 00:02.423
And when we come back,

00:02.430 --> 00:03.454
Our own keith bradshaw

00:03.469 --> 00:04.369
Has a special report

00:04.370 --> 00:05.792
On which southern california
restaurants

00:05.800 --> 00:07.962
Aren't making the grade
when it comes

00:07.970 --> 00:09.392
To serving
sanitary meals.

00:09.410 --> 00:12.004
Good thing I've
already had dinner.

00:12.010 --> 00:15.708
Stay with us.
We'll be right back.

00:15.710 --> 00:16.939
Woman: And we're out.

00:16.950 --> 00:20.375
[indistinct chatter]

00:22.180 --> 00:23.909
Hey, john.

00:29.020 --> 00:31.352
Ok. You're good.

00:55.620 --> 00:57.679
Man: Sorry.
Let me just--

00:57.690 --> 01:01.809
There we go.
Good. You're good.

01:15.440 --> 01:17.693
My daughter.

01:17.710 --> 01:18.905
Oh, my god.

01:18.910 --> 01:21.038
Oh, my god.
Emma. Oh, my god!

01:21.040 --> 01:21.836
John, what happened?

01:21.840 --> 01:23.103
And we're back
in 3, 2...

01:23.110 --> 01:25.249
No. No, no, no, no.
He's at my house!

01:25.250 --> 01:26.809
Somebody, call
the police!

01:26.820 --> 01:27.776
Please help me!

01:27.780 --> 01:30.112
Get the police
to my house now, now!

01:30.120 --> 01:31.281
Woman: John, what's wrong?

01:31.290 --> 01:32.439
He's gonna hurt
my daughter.

01:32.460 --> 01:34.189
He's gonna hurt my
daughter. Help me! Help me!

01:34.190 --> 01:36.284
We, uh, apologize
to our viewers.

01:36.290 --> 01:37.928
We are experiencing an
emergency situation here.

01:37.930 --> 01:41.355
Help me!
Somebody, help me!

02:07.390 --> 02:08.515
Morning.

02:08.520 --> 02:09.988
Morning, jack.

02:09.990 --> 02:11.355
I just wanted to
say thanks

02:11.360 --> 02:14.330
For the other night,
confiding in me.

02:14.330 --> 02:16.822
I know it's not an
easy thing for you to do,

02:16.830 --> 02:19.697
And I appreciate it.

02:19.700 --> 02:22.135
Thank you
for listening.

02:22.140 --> 02:23.494
Question. Who else
in the office

02:23.510 --> 02:25.160
Because janice knows
about your real name

02:25.170 --> 02:27.036
And your life
in seattle?

02:27.040 --> 02:29.475
Well, her, amanda,
and you.

02:29.480 --> 02:31.744
I'd like to keep it
that way for now.

02:31.750 --> 02:33.605
Of course.

02:35.380 --> 02:38.213
Michelle, huh?
I can see it.

02:38.220 --> 02:42.714
I like beth, but
michelle works, too.

02:44.490 --> 02:46.822
Come in.
Shut the door.

02:48.760 --> 02:50.489
I just spoke
with perry whitley's father.

02:50.500 --> 02:52.867
He refuses to file
a missing persons report.

02:52.870 --> 02:55.464
He expressed his concern
but is more concerned

02:55.470 --> 02:57.632
About keeping it quiet.

02:59.840 --> 03:01.376
This just in.

03:01.380 --> 03:03.178
Thanks.

03:03.180 --> 03:04.602
How's your friend tracy?

03:04.610 --> 03:06.271
She left town. She's
staying with a friend

03:06.280 --> 03:07.543
Till we can find
perry.

03:07.550 --> 03:09.644
Can we put out an apb
based on the assault charge?

03:09.650 --> 03:11.049
No. Perry's father
posted bail.

03:11.050 --> 03:13.041
There's nothing we can do
until he fails

03:13.060 --> 03:14.482
To show up
for his prelim.

03:14.490 --> 03:16.584
If we want to put
perry away,

03:16.590 --> 03:19.059
We have to build
a New case.

03:20.400 --> 03:22.960
Somebody, call the police.
Please help me!

03:22.970 --> 03:24.790
Get the police
to my house now! Now!

03:24.800 --> 03:26.165
What are you
watching?

03:26.170 --> 03:27.467
You remember john bardo?

03:27.470 --> 03:28.733
Channel 12
news guy.

03:28.740 --> 03:30.139
Last night,
he received a text

03:30.140 --> 03:31.062
During the broadcast.

03:31.070 --> 03:32.435
It was a video taken
from inside

03:32.440 --> 03:33.862
His daughter's closet.

03:33.880 --> 03:34.904
Bardo freaks out
on air.

03:34.910 --> 03:36.605
Turns out, his daughter
was at the movies.

03:36.610 --> 03:37.634
She was safe,
thank god.

03:37.650 --> 03:39.300
The video was recorded
a week prior,

03:39.320 --> 03:40.503
And the text came
from a burner,

03:40.520 --> 03:41.646
So it couldn't
be traced.

03:41.650 --> 03:43.049
We handled a stalking case
for him two years ago.

03:43.050 --> 03:45.280
Man obsessed with
bardo from his newscast.

03:45.290 --> 03:46.985
Broke into his house,
tried to kill him, right?

03:46.990 --> 03:48.856
Yeah. Sam russell,
a crime stringer.

03:48.860 --> 03:50.749
He chased crime scenes
and traffic accidents.

03:50.760 --> 03:52.159
He started supplying
tips to bardo

03:52.160 --> 03:53.719
When he was still
a field reporter.

03:53.730 --> 03:55.220
Sam idolized bardo,

03:55.230 --> 03:56.197
Became obsessed with him,

03:56.200 --> 03:57.759
And then when he started
stalking him,

03:57.770 --> 04:00.421
I was notified. Sam was
released 3 months ago.

04:00.440 --> 04:02.192
John on tv: Somebody,
call the police!

04:02.200 --> 04:03.065
Please help me!

04:03.070 --> 04:04.333
Get the police
to my house now! Now!

04:04.340 --> 04:05.865
The police are trying
to locate russell now.

04:05.870 --> 04:07.929
He's not at home, but he
has a clean probation report.

04:07.940 --> 04:09.704
Bardo could have
a new stalker.

04:09.710 --> 04:11.849
You know, these news
people, they get this a lot.

04:11.850 --> 04:13.249
All right. We'll talk
to bardo.

04:13.250 --> 04:15.878
Jack, let's go. You
guys, find us our stringer.

04:15.880 --> 04:17.745
Beth: According
to the exif file,

04:17.750 --> 04:19.387
This video was
taken last week.

04:19.390 --> 04:21.916
My ex-wife linda and I,
we share custody.

04:21.920 --> 04:24.651
Emma stays with me
every other week.

04:24.660 --> 04:28.255
It was him, wasn't
it? Same russell?

04:28.260 --> 04:29.227
Have you arrested him?

04:29.230 --> 04:30.925
We'll talk to him,
but we may have to

04:30.930 --> 04:32.125
Treat this
as a new threat.

04:32.130 --> 04:33.598
You may have
another stalker.

04:33.600 --> 04:37.093
Jack: Have you noticed any other
attention recently from your fans,

04:37.110 --> 04:39.636
People in your life,
ex-wife?

04:39.640 --> 04:42.302
What happened
with your marriage?

04:42.310 --> 04:43.471
A man broke
into my home

04:43.480 --> 04:45.903
And tried to kill me
in front of my wife.

04:45.910 --> 04:48.049
After that, we couldn't
make it work.

04:48.050 --> 04:49.074
My whole life fell apart.

04:49.080 --> 04:50.946
I still look
over my shoulder.

04:50.950 --> 04:54.887
We're on good terms
because of my daughter.

04:54.890 --> 04:56.289
His ex linda is
a sweetheart.

04:56.290 --> 04:57.485
She couldn't be
behind this.

04:57.490 --> 05:01.051
And, lauren, how long
have you two been together?

05:01.060 --> 05:02.755
4 or 5 weeks. Why?

05:02.770 --> 05:05.330
Well, it's routine, hon.
They have to ask.

05:05.330 --> 05:06.764
And you live here
with john?

05:06.770 --> 05:08.568
No. No. I just
came over last night

05:08.570 --> 05:09.696
When I heard
what happened.

05:09.710 --> 05:12.702
Any signs of break-in,
anything moved or taken?

05:12.710 --> 05:14.303
Look. It has to be
sam russell.

05:14.310 --> 05:16.130
There is no way
I have two stalkers.

05:16.150 --> 05:17.732
I mean, come on.
What are the odds?

05:17.750 --> 05:18.808
You'd be surprised.

05:18.810 --> 05:20.574
People in your profession
often attract

05:20.580 --> 05:21.775
Obsessive personalities.

05:21.780 --> 05:23.418
They notified me,
all right?

05:23.420 --> 05:24.546
He was released
3 months ago.

05:24.550 --> 05:27.781
I know, and I will
talk to him personally.

05:27.790 --> 05:31.090
We'll get to the truth,
I promise.

05:31.090 --> 05:32.979
[sighs]

05:33.630 --> 05:35.689
Beth: Why were you
hiding from us?

05:35.700 --> 05:38.567
I knew you were
gonna accuse me.

05:38.570 --> 05:39.526
I know what
happened.

05:39.540 --> 05:41.793
John bardo's
the news story of the day.

05:41.800 --> 05:43.063
I'm not your guy.

05:43.070 --> 05:45.801
I would never hurt
john or his family.

05:45.810 --> 05:47.107
I respect the man.

05:47.110 --> 05:49.431
Funny way of showing
your admiration,

05:49.450 --> 05:51.179
Showing up at his house
with a gun.

05:51.180 --> 05:54.571
That was a misunderstanding
two years ago.

05:54.580 --> 05:56.810
I went over to his house
to talk to him.

05:56.820 --> 06:00.586
I practice my
second amendment rights.

06:00.590 --> 06:02.684
I would never
hurt john.

06:02.690 --> 06:04.249
Where were you
last night?

06:04.260 --> 06:06.251
Home, editing.

06:06.260 --> 06:09.059
I have a crime blog.
It takes up all my time.

06:09.060 --> 06:10.255
And the night
of the 24th?

06:10.270 --> 06:13.524
That was the night of the
big accident on the 101.

06:13.540 --> 06:15.269
I was there shooting
"b" roll.

06:15.270 --> 06:17.261
Can anyone vouch
for you?

06:17.270 --> 06:21.400
No, but I'm not
stalking john.

06:21.410 --> 06:24.710
You guys should be out there
looking for the real stalker.

06:24.710 --> 06:26.804
- John could be in
serious trouble, you know.

06:26.820 --> 06:32.680
He's a good guy, and someone
has to watch out for him.

06:34.620 --> 06:36.816
Beth: I'm not convinced
sam is reformed,

06:36.830 --> 06:39.788
But I'm not so sure
the psychology adds up.

06:39.800 --> 06:41.825
Sam is a intimacy-seeking
stalker.

06:41.830 --> 06:43.924
He wants a closer
connection to john.

06:43.930 --> 06:45.091
He only escalated
two years ago

06:45.100 --> 06:46.465
Because john rejected
his help.

06:46.470 --> 06:50.293
I just don't see him sending
threatening texts or videos.

06:50.310 --> 06:52.961
That seems like something we
see more in resentful stalkers.

06:52.980 --> 06:56.075
I checked the alibis for the
ex-wife, the new girlfriend.

06:56.080 --> 06:57.002
Neither have motives.

06:57.010 --> 06:58.705
His daughter seems
well-adjusted.

06:58.710 --> 06:59.871
It's not a prank.

06:59.880 --> 07:01.416
Ok. Then john has
a new stalker.

07:01.420 --> 07:03.218
Let's go with that
for now.

07:03.220 --> 07:04.517
News anchors are
the most common

07:04.520 --> 07:05.544
Of celebrity stalking cases.

07:05.550 --> 07:07.848
They're in everybody's
living room,

07:07.860 --> 07:09.009
Looking
through the camera

07:09.020 --> 07:10.579
Into the eyes
of the people watching them.

07:10.590 --> 07:12.354
It's intimate.
They become fixated.

07:12.360 --> 07:14.249
They really think
they have a relationship

07:14.260 --> 07:15.227
With these people.

07:15.230 --> 07:16.595
Well, ben and I
went to the news station.

07:16.600 --> 07:18.329
We grilled the whole
staff, co-workers.

07:18.330 --> 07:21.595
No one had heard or seen
an unusual fan, nothing.

07:21.600 --> 07:22.965
What's that?

07:22.970 --> 07:23.698
What?

07:23.710 --> 07:26.065
Go back
frame by frame.

07:26.770 --> 07:28.135
There.
What is it?

07:28.140 --> 07:29.471
Can you enhance it?

07:29.480 --> 07:32.006
You see it?
Reflection in the mirror?

07:32.010 --> 07:33.546
I can better that.

07:33.550 --> 07:35.245
Someone inside wearing
a dark jacket.

07:35.250 --> 07:36.877
Is that a logo?
Partial logo.

07:36.890 --> 07:37.914
Can you decipher it?

07:37.920 --> 07:39.012
Yeah. Give me
some time.

07:39.020 --> 07:40.886
Beth: Janice, let's get
a unit on john's house

07:40.890 --> 07:42.119
And his ex-wife
and his daughter.

07:42.120 --> 07:45.829
Let's keep them safe till
we can figure something out.

07:47.800 --> 07:50.656
How's emma?

07:50.670 --> 07:52.559
Ok. Well,
the security company's

07:52.570 --> 07:55.232
Gonna be with you guys
24 hours a day

07:55.240 --> 07:57.060
Until they catch this guy.

07:57.070 --> 08:00.608
Look. I'm--I'm
really sorry, linda.

08:00.610 --> 08:03.830
I know, but I all I want is
for you and emma to be safe.

08:03.850 --> 08:05.875
You know that.

08:05.880 --> 08:09.771
Yeah. Ahem.
Ok. Bye.

08:10.650 --> 08:11.913
Was that your ex?

08:11.920 --> 08:13.888
Yeah. Ahem.

08:13.890 --> 08:15.654
What did she want?

08:15.660 --> 08:20.222
Hmm. I, um--I hired
a security team

08:20.230 --> 08:23.256
To watch after he
and emma.

08:23.270 --> 08:25.830
You're a good man,
john,

08:25.830 --> 08:28.128
But I don't know why you
don't do the same thing

08:28.140 --> 08:30.563
At your own house.

08:30.570 --> 08:32.129
I did.

08:32.140 --> 08:33.801
Security will be
here tomorrow.

08:33.809 --> 08:36.404
You know, you didn't
have to stay here tonight.

08:36.409 --> 08:38.947
I know all this is
really freaking you out.

08:38.950 --> 08:42.544
I'm not gonna
leave you like she did.

08:56.760 --> 08:59.070
[thud]

08:59.070 --> 09:00.822
What was that?

09:03.440 --> 09:05.465
I don't know.

09:07.070 --> 09:08.140
Where are you going?

09:08.140 --> 09:10.700
Stay here. Lock the
door and call the police.

09:10.710 --> 09:11.541
John, don't!

09:11.550 --> 09:13.177
Lauren, I am not
a victim.

09:13.180 --> 09:15.877
Lock the door
and call the police.

10:26.220 --> 10:28.655
You son of a bitch!

10:28.660 --> 10:30.412
Get out here!

10:30.430 --> 10:32.626
Come on!
Show your face!

10:34.560 --> 10:36.756
Where are you?

10:44.540 --> 10:45.666
Oh, my god.

10:45.670 --> 10:48.105
Lauren, lauren, lauren!

10:48.110 --> 10:49.771
He's in the room
with you!

10:49.780 --> 10:51.100
He's in the bathroom!

10:51.110 --> 10:52.441
Unlock the door!

10:52.450 --> 10:54.509
Aah! Aah!
Lauren!

10:54.520 --> 10:57.478
[screaming]

11:00.390 --> 11:03.917
Aah!
Lapd. Don't move!

11:04.790 --> 11:06.929
Stay on the ground.

11:08.560 --> 11:10.654
You got him?

11:16.670 --> 11:17.592
I'm not lying

11:17.610 --> 11:19.601
Why did you break
into john's house?

11:19.610 --> 11:21.032
He needed my help.

11:21.040 --> 11:23.202
You attacked
his girlfriend.

11:23.210 --> 11:26.100
John needs me.
He doesn't need her.

11:26.110 --> 11:27.202
Is he gay?

11:27.220 --> 11:29.109
Is it romantic
obsession?

11:29.120 --> 11:30.349
No. He worships him.

11:30.350 --> 11:32.819
He doesn't want anyone
to be near john but him.

11:32.820 --> 11:33.946
No one's good enough.

11:33.960 --> 11:35.883
You didn't answer
the question.

11:35.890 --> 11:38.450
After I spoke
with you guys,

11:38.460 --> 11:40.428
I got scared for john,

11:40.430 --> 11:41.989
So I had to find out.

11:42.000 --> 11:44.423
You broke probation.

11:44.430 --> 11:47.092
You're going
back to prison.

11:47.100 --> 11:48.864
I'm sorry.

11:48.870 --> 11:50.167
Don't send me back.

11:50.170 --> 11:52.161
I ca--I can't
follow the news

11:52.170 --> 11:53.535
If you send me back.

11:53.540 --> 11:57.704
Please! I-I screwed up
just the once.

11:57.710 --> 11:59.041
This guy's
not well.

11:59.050 --> 12:02.350
But I'm not so sure he's
the one we're looking for.

12:02.350 --> 12:04.910
Look. C-c-can I--
can I go to a city jail?

12:04.920 --> 12:08.345
If you send me upstate,
I can't get channel 12.

12:08.360 --> 12:10.112
I won't do it again,
I swe--

12:10.130 --> 12:11.689
Is john back there?

12:11.690 --> 12:14.330
Jo--john, I would never
hurt you, john!

12:14.330 --> 12:16.094
You know this!
Tell them!

12:16.100 --> 12:18.398
We confiscated his video
and recording equipment

12:18.400 --> 12:19.993
He had quite the setup.
Looks like he's been

12:20.000 --> 12:22.059
Following
john and his family.

12:22.070 --> 12:23.299
Any video
of john's daughter?

12:23.310 --> 12:24.630
None from her bedroom,
but there is footage

12:24.640 --> 12:26.631
Of her, john,
john's ex-wife,

12:26.640 --> 12:27.710
And most
of his colleagues.

12:27.710 --> 12:29.508
So sam was stalking
by proxy until last night.

12:29.510 --> 12:31.137
That's how he's
getting his fix

12:31.150 --> 12:32.470
Without violating
his tro.

12:32.480 --> 12:34.676
He was stalking
everyone around the person

12:34.680 --> 12:35.670
He was obsessed with.

12:35.680 --> 12:37.273
I'm still combing
through the footage,

12:37.290 --> 12:39.748
But I found one thing
of interest.

12:39.760 --> 12:40.750
Ben: An altercation.

12:40.760 --> 12:41.818
Jack: Who's
the other guy?

12:41.820 --> 12:44.289
Keith bradshaw,
field correspondent.

12:44.290 --> 12:45.758
They're arguing
about something.

12:45.760 --> 12:47.558
Ben: A little digging,
and I found out

12:47.560 --> 12:48.550
Keith was up for anchor,

12:48.560 --> 12:49.698
But john got
the job instead.

12:49.700 --> 12:51.259
So maybe keith
seeks retribution

12:51.270 --> 12:52.396
For perceived
injustice,

12:52.400 --> 12:53.822
Starts stalking
his work colleague.

12:53.840 --> 12:55.467
Classic case
of workplace stalking.

12:55.470 --> 12:59.600
Which usually escalates
quickly to violence.

12:59.610 --> 13:00.566
Damn. That hurt.

13:00.580 --> 13:02.799
John never mentioned
any co-worker dispute.

13:02.810 --> 13:03.936
He clocked him.

13:03.950 --> 13:05.475
Well, no charges
were ever filed.

13:05.480 --> 13:06.572
What's the date
on that?

13:06.580 --> 13:08.344
December 14,
around the same time

13:08.350 --> 13:09.340
John was promoted.

13:09.350 --> 13:10.442
Maybe keith
was jealous.

13:10.450 --> 13:12.418
I spoke to the station's
hr department myself.

13:12.420 --> 13:15.014
There was no record
of a co-worker rivalry.

13:15.020 --> 13:16.488
Most victims of
workplace stalking

13:16.490 --> 13:17.480
Won't run
to the boss.

13:17.490 --> 13:18.821
They're afraid
of getting fired.

13:18.830 --> 13:20.059
Ben, go through
this footage.

13:20.060 --> 13:21.425
Let's see who else
we can link to john.

13:21.430 --> 13:24.092
In the meantime, we'll
talk to keith bradshaw.

13:27.170 --> 13:30.538
[ball bouncing]

13:38.580 --> 13:41.003
Told you
I'd be back.

13:41.020 --> 13:42.545
What do you want,
a medal?

13:42.550 --> 13:45.986
No. No. I just
want to talk.

13:45.990 --> 13:50.712
Have you thought any about
what we discussed last time?

13:50.730 --> 13:51.720
It won't work.

13:51.730 --> 13:56.099
Yes, it will.
I know it will.

13:56.100 --> 13:59.024
Why do you want
to help me?

13:59.030 --> 14:00.725
The two of us,

14:00.740 --> 14:02.538
We're like-minded,
right?

14:02.540 --> 14:06.636
We--we share a--
a kinship of suffering,

14:06.640 --> 14:09.109
A mutual obsession.

14:09.110 --> 14:11.499
Michelle.

14:11.510 --> 14:13.604
Tell me about her.

14:21.520 --> 14:23.818
She changed her name?

14:25.960 --> 14:27.553
Yes.

14:27.560 --> 14:29.198
She goes
by beth davis.

14:29.200 --> 14:33.592
She's a detective--
well, lieutenant actually.

14:33.600 --> 14:37.264
She's in charge of lapd's
threat assessment unit.

14:37.270 --> 14:40.570
She investigates
stalking cases.

14:43.210 --> 14:44.280
Is she married?

14:44.280 --> 14:48.615
