because of his part in it.

29:34.030 --> 29:36.931
No wonder he didn't tell
us about a previous stalker.

29:36.940 --> 29:38.396
He was worried about
losing his job again.

29:38.410 --> 29:41.300
And get this--one of the gifts
he used to hand out to his fans

29:41.310 --> 29:44.132
Were bradbury university
shirts.

29:44.150 --> 29:45.402
I just spoke
with chicago pd.

29:45.410 --> 29:47.401
The print we found
on the casing isn't keith's.

29:47.410 --> 29:48.673
It belongs
to a woman.

29:48.680 --> 29:49.909
Let me guess--
candice donovan.

29:49.920 --> 29:52.378
She was arrested for violating
a tro keith had against her.

29:52.390 --> 29:54.142
They're e-mailing
me the report.

29:54.160 --> 29:55.980
So she was stalking keith in
chicago and then came here

29:55.990 --> 29:57.879
And started
stalking john?

29:57.890 --> 29:59.119
Stalking's not
territorial.

29:59.130 --> 30:01.053
We see people travel
thousands of miles

30:01.060 --> 30:02.084
Across state lines.

30:02.100 --> 30:04.592
I just got the police report
on donvoan.

30:04.600 --> 30:07.262
Um, you guys
need to see this.

30:10.340 --> 30:11.967
Meet candice donovan.

30:11.970 --> 30:15.201
That's john's
girlfriend lauren.

30:15.210 --> 30:17.201
And with all that
sunshine in the forecast,

30:17.210 --> 30:19.702
It like it's gonna be
a beautiful week.

30:19.710 --> 30:22.372
Well, that about wraps
it up for us, folks.

30:22.380 --> 30:24.644
From all of us here
at channel 12,

30:24.650 --> 30:25.742
Have a pleasant evening.

30:25.750 --> 30:27.980
Stay tuned for
the "world news report,"

30:27.990 --> 30:29.913
Coming up next.

30:29.920 --> 30:32.651
Woman: And we're clear.

30:38.260 --> 30:41.025
Hey, john.
Can I grab your mike?

30:47.240 --> 30:48.332
Oht

30:48.340 --> 30:49.808
Whoa.

30:49.810 --> 30:52.177
Hey. Uh, john. Look.

30:52.180 --> 30:54.171
I know you've been going
through a horrible time,

30:54.180 --> 30:58.549
And, uh, I've been
a complete ass to you, so--

30:58.550 --> 31:02.589
Look. I just--I just
want this to be over.

31:02.590 --> 31:03.910
John.

31:03.920 --> 31:05.149
Yeah?

31:05.160 --> 31:09.256
I'm not stalking
you, man, I swear.

31:10.700 --> 31:12.555
Ahem.

31:30.750 --> 31:34.243
Ugh. Sss.

31:34.260 --> 31:36.149
[sighs]

31:40.060 --> 31:41.983
[exhales]

31:46.370 --> 31:47.326
Lauren, hey.
Hey.

31:47.330 --> 31:48.866
What are you doing
here, sweetheart?

31:48.870 --> 31:51.134
I just came by
to check on you.

31:51.140 --> 31:52.733
You know, I mean, after
everything you've been through,

31:52.740 --> 31:54.560
Shouldn't you have
taken some time off?

31:54.580 --> 31:57.208
Oh. Yeah, well,
this job's the only thing

31:57.210 --> 31:58.803
Keeping me sane.

31:58.810 --> 32:02.303
But you were supposed
to be in the hospital.

32:02.320 --> 32:03.674
You were supposed to
take time off.

32:03.680 --> 32:06.047
I mean, that's what you did
when you were stalked before.

32:06.050 --> 32:08.610
You took several
months off.

32:08.620 --> 32:09.815
What's wrong with you?

32:09.820 --> 32:11.288
Mental duress.
Remember?

32:11.290 --> 32:12.155
I looked it up online.

32:12.160 --> 32:15.380
What are--what are
you talking about?

32:15.400 --> 32:17.721
It's keith's turn now.

32:17.730 --> 32:19.459
We're done playing,
john.

32:19.470 --> 32:21.290
It's time for you
to go away.

32:21.300 --> 32:25.168
You should know
I actually liked you,

32:25.170 --> 32:28.299
But I love keith.

32:28.310 --> 32:29.630
Wait. Look, lauren.

32:29.640 --> 32:31.677
That's not my name.

32:31.680 --> 32:33.341
Look. Just--just--
just wait.

32:33.350 --> 32:34.806
John, do you have
a second?

32:34.820 --> 32:35.946
Adele, run!

32:35.950 --> 32:37.315
[gunshot]

32:37.320 --> 32:39.573
Unh!

32:39.590 --> 32:42.981
[adele screaming]

32:44.820 --> 32:45.912
Man:
Is anybody hurt?

32:45.930 --> 32:47.079
Woman: Go back
to your office!

32:47.090 --> 32:48.785
I'm gonna call
the police.

32:48.800 --> 32:50.689
[shouting]

32:50.700 --> 32:52.020
Ohh!

32:52.030 --> 32:54.692
Man: Somebody's
got a gun!

33:03.080 --> 33:05.003
[sirens]

33:05.010 --> 33:07.104
She's barricaded herself
inside of a dressing room

33:07.110 --> 33:08.248
On the north side
of the building.

33:08.250 --> 33:10.969
One hostage,
newscaster john bardo,

33:10.990 --> 33:12.640
Being held
at gunpoint.

33:12.650 --> 33:14.015
Are you getting
everyone else out?

33:14.020 --> 33:16.011
We're evacuating to
the parking lot right now.

33:16.020 --> 33:17.510
Where's
the control room?

33:17.520 --> 33:19.113
Right this way.

33:19.130 --> 33:20.382
Beth: John just finished
his newscast.

33:20.390 --> 33:22.882
He might still have
his mike on.

33:22.900 --> 33:24.459
Pull up john's mike.

33:24.470 --> 33:26.723
Oh. OKk.

33:26.730 --> 33:29.199
John: Lauren, whatever
your name is, this is crazy.

33:29.200 --> 33:30.793
Lauren: Don't
call me crazy.

33:30.800 --> 33:32.234
No. You're not crazy.

33:32.240 --> 33:35.335
They know you're here. You're
never gonna get out of this.

33:35.340 --> 33:37.308
Well, if I don't get
out, you don't get out.

33:37.310 --> 33:39.574
J-just lower the gun,
please, ok, hon?

33:39.580 --> 33:41.639
Ugh. Don't call me hon.
I hate it when you

33:41.650 --> 33:42.640
Call me hon.

33:42.650 --> 33:45.278
Only keith
calls me hon.

33:45.290 --> 33:47.782
Ok. Then--then you
go find him.

33:47.790 --> 33:49.315
Go find him.
Be with him.

33:49.320 --> 33:50.310
I'll stay here.

33:50.320 --> 33:51.515
John, this is beth davis.

33:51.530 --> 33:52.884
Listen to me.
Stop provoking her.

33:52.890 --> 33:54.688
She's delusional.
She thinks she's

33:54.700 --> 33:56.225
In a relationship
with keith.

33:56.230 --> 33:58.255
Affirm that.

33:58.270 --> 34:01.365
You're, uh, candice.

34:01.370 --> 34:02.769
You're keith's candice,

34:02.770 --> 34:04.260
The one he talks about.

34:04.270 --> 34:06.068
Yes. From chicago.

34:06.070 --> 34:08.129
Candice from chicago.

34:08.139 --> 34:09.630
How do you
know that?

34:09.639 --> 34:10.675
Beth: "keith told me."

34:10.679 --> 34:12.739
Keith talks about you
all the time.

34:12.750 --> 34:16.106
What has he
told you?

34:16.120 --> 34:17.975
Tell her.
You're doing great.

34:17.989 --> 34:19.411
She thinks she's
in love with him.

34:19.420 --> 34:20.717
That's why she's
doing this.

34:20.719 --> 34:24.213
Well...He told me how
much that you love him.

34:24.219 --> 34:25.415
It's incredibly romantic.

34:25.429 --> 34:28.922
I-I wish I had
someone like that.

34:28.929 --> 34:32.230
What keith and I have
is very special.

34:32.230 --> 34:34.221
How'd you meet?

34:39.070 --> 34:41.129
When we first met, we
were in my living room

34:41.139 --> 34:42.107
Back in chicago.

34:42.110 --> 34:44.909
Keith was out in the
field doing a report,

34:44.909 --> 34:46.309
And he was looking
right at me.

34:46.310 --> 34:47.902
He used to send
me messages,

34:47.920 --> 34:50.139
Secret messages
when he was reporting.

34:50.150 --> 34:54.188
He knew I'd be watching
the tv. I would understand--

34:54.190 --> 34:55.248
[thump]

34:55.260 --> 34:56.216
Somebody's outside.

34:56.219 --> 34:58.587
I'll kill him,
do you hear me?

34:58.590 --> 34:59.853
Tell them to stand down!

34:59.860 --> 35:00.884
Rescue team,
stand down.

35:00.890 --> 35:02.187
Get keith bradshaw
in here!

35:02.200 --> 35:03.690
No! Nobody's out there!

35:03.700 --> 35:04.849
How do you know?

35:04.870 --> 35:05.723
What are you doing?

35:05.730 --> 35:07.391
Is that something
in your ear?

35:07.400 --> 35:09.937
Oh. I will blow your
head off, so help me.

35:09.940 --> 35:11.294
Give it to me.
Give you what?

35:11.310 --> 35:12.436
The mike in your ear.

35:12.440 --> 35:14.169
John's still wired. Beth
will walk you through it.

35:14.170 --> 35:16.207
Wait. Tell her that keith
wants to talk to her.

35:16.210 --> 35:17.075
Ok. Wait, wait.

35:17.080 --> 35:20.072
Keith is--he's
in the control room.

35:20.080 --> 35:23.175
Yeah. He wants
to talk to you.

35:26.120 --> 35:28.714
Ahem. Um...

35:28.720 --> 35:29.744
Hello?

35:29.760 --> 35:31.182
Keith. Hey, man.

35:31.190 --> 35:34.125
Yeah. Hold on.
Candice is right here.

35:34.130 --> 35:38.749
Take this
and take this, too.

35:38.770 --> 35:40.420
Here. Talk to him.

35:40.430 --> 35:42.762
Go ahead.
Talk to him.

35:42.770 --> 35:46.331
Keith: Is this candice?

35:46.340 --> 35:48.434
Keith?

35:48.440 --> 35:51.899
Hey, baby. It's me.

35:51.910 --> 35:54.641
You know I really want
to be with you, right,

35:54.650 --> 35:57.950
But if you hurt john,
then--then we can't be together.

35:57.950 --> 35:59.213
"They'll put you
away forever.

35:59.220 --> 36:00.449
I don't want to
lose you."

36:00.450 --> 36:01.747
They'll put you
away forever,

36:01.760 --> 36:03.854
And, baby, I don't
want to lose you.

36:03.860 --> 36:07.728
I want you to put
the gun down.

36:11.800 --> 36:14.121
Agh! Unh!

36:14.130 --> 36:15.495
Initiate, initiate!

36:15.500 --> 36:17.059
Man on radio:
All teams, go!

36:17.070 --> 36:20.267
Move!
Drop it now!

36:20.270 --> 36:23.308
This is why you
don't understand.

36:23.310 --> 36:26.575
This was for keith.
I love keith.

36:28.610 --> 36:31.978
[music playing]

37:07.290 --> 37:12.080
Ben: So keith's stalker
followed him to |.A. From chicago.

37:12.090 --> 37:13.160
True love.

37:13.160 --> 37:15.925
[cell phone ringing]

37:23.370 --> 37:25.134
Hello?

37:25.140 --> 37:27.939
Ray: Hello, michelle.

37:27.940 --> 37:30.170
It's been a long time.

37:34.810 --> 37:37.279
I've missed you.

37:40.620 --> 37:44.011
Are you guys gonna
fill me in or what?

37:44.020 --> 37:46.079
Is perry with you?

37:46.090 --> 37:49.788
You already know the
answer to that, michelle,

37:49.800 --> 37:52.690
Or would you
prefer beth?

37:57.300 --> 37:58.768
Tell me where
you are, ray.

37:58.770 --> 38:00.829
I want to see you.

38:00.840 --> 38:03.730
And I want to see
you, too.

38:03.740 --> 38:06.710
Soon, michelle, soon.

38:13.290 --> 38:14.985
Beth?

38:16.890 --> 38:19.882
What is it?

38:19.890 --> 38:23.155
It was ray.

38:23.160 --> 38:26.528
[music playing]

38:38.940 --> 38:40.476
Everything looks fine.

38:40.480 --> 38:42.403
I'll be outside
in the car.

38:42.420 --> 38:44.639
Great. Thanks.

38:53.160 --> 38:55.754
[beeping]

39:08.210 --> 39:10.975
[knock on door]

39:16.180 --> 39:18.740
[beeping]

39:20.650 --> 39:21.788
I was gonna come alone,

39:21.790 --> 39:26.853
But they wouldn't take
no for an answer.

39:26.860 --> 39:29.921
Slumber party,
game night, movie.

39:29.930 --> 39:33.025
It's whatever
you want it to be.

39:33.630 --> 39:36.998
Ben: They told me.
I had no idea.

39:37.000 --> 39:39.094
I'm sorry, beth.

39:39.110 --> 39:41.204
Hope you like
pepperoni.

39:51.280 --> 39:53.044
You don't have to
do this.

39:53.050 --> 39:54.779
There's
a unit outside.

39:54.790 --> 39:56.610
You asked
for your help.

39:56.620 --> 39:57.883
This is help.

39:57.890 --> 39:59.255
[Janice laughing]

39:59.260 --> 40:00.557
Boo-yah!

40:00.560 --> 40:01.356
Here you go.

40:01.360 --> 40:04.057
In the form of beer
and pizza?

40:04.060 --> 40:06.825
It's not all
about you.

40:09.970 --> 40:12.735
Thank you.

40:12.740 --> 40:13.639
What we got?

40:13.640 --> 40:14.801
Ben: Get in on this.
Pepperoni.

40:14.810 --> 40:16.005
That's what I call
a party.

40:16.010 --> 40:19.401
Beth, grab it.
It's cold.

40:19.410 --> 40:22.801
[music continues]
